          <br />
          the best
          <br />
          quotes.
        </div>
      </div>
    <div class="col-4 slogan">
      It's a quote gets quote world out there.
    </div> 
    <div class="col-5 links">
      <%= link_to 'Contribute', '#' %>
      <%= link_to 'About', '#' %>
    </div>
    </header>

    <hr />

    <br class="clear" />

  <div class="container">
    <%= yield %>
  </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-6">
            This isn't enough, I need more
          </div>
          <div class="col-6 footer-blurb">
            Proudly created by LLCoolDane with the help of Vanderbilt coding bootcamp.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>




